WEBVTT

00:02.959 --> 00:04.726
BOY:
Tommy's is full of holes,

00:04.794 --> 00:06.561
and the tail is falling off.

00:06.853 --> 00:09.454
I want my own, just like Fess Parker.

00:09.522 --> 00:11.823
Is that all Christmas
is to you, presents?

00:11.891 --> 00:13.758
Put this in the can.

00:14.778 --> 00:16.928
Ho, ho, ho!

00:16.996 --> 00:18.397
Merry Christmas!

00:18.465 --> 00:20.033
Now, you be good and listen

00:20.101 --> 00:21.668
to your mom and maybe that

00:21.736 --> 00:24.271
coonskin cap will be under
your tree Christmas morning,

00:24.339 --> 00:25.939
huh?
MOM: They're closed.

00:26.007 --> 00:27.975
Come on, I think the Star Market
is open until 9:00.

00:28.043 --> 00:30.778
(switches clank, Christmas music
winds down and stops)

00:33.515 --> 00:35.350
Whew!

00:37.552 --> 00:39.520
(sniffles, sighs)

00:39.588 --> 00:41.555
He's gonna be pretty steamed at you

00:41.623 --> 00:43.391
if he doesn't get that hat.

00:44.626 --> 00:45.959
Well, if he's good enough,

00:46.027 --> 00:47.394
his mother will end up giving it to him.

00:47.462 --> 00:49.129
If he's naughty, he'll blame himself.

00:49.197 --> 00:50.631
It's never your fault, hmm?

00:50.699 --> 00:52.199
It's all about the list.

00:52.267 --> 00:54.235
Some kid doesn't get
their Renco Frogman,

00:54.303 --> 00:55.970
but you can't blame Santa.

00:56.038 --> 00:58.039
Pretty nifty win-win
you set up for yourself.

00:58.107 --> 01:00.476
Hey, buddy... I'm just ringing
the bell two nights a week,

01:00.543 --> 01:02.612
to get out of the house
till my wife falls asleep.

01:02.679 --> 01:03.646
(gunshot)

01:06.717 --> 01:08.552
(four gunshots)

01:12.090 --> 01:14.826
("We Wish You a Merry
Christmas" playing)

