01:26.240 --> 01:28.007
♪ ♪

01:31.713 --> 01:33.447
GIRL:
Santa?

01:34.683 --> 01:36.851
Oh.

01:36.918 --> 01:38.919
Hi, sweetie.

01:38.987 --> 01:41.256
This is a fantastic train set.

01:41.324 --> 01:44.126
The farm even has tiny little hay bales.

01:44.193 --> 01:45.093
It's my dad's.

01:45.161 --> 01:46.061
Mm-hmm.

01:46.129 --> 01:46.928
Where's your beard?

01:49.132 --> 01:51.233
I shaved. It was scratchy.

01:51.300 --> 01:53.001
Why are you here?

01:53.069 --> 01:55.370
Christmas isn't for six days.

01:57.139 --> 02:00.475
That's what you get
for letting Rudolph organize

02:00.543 --> 02:02.177
your calendar.
And it would

02:02.245 --> 02:04.479
explain the lack of milk and cookies.

02:04.547 --> 02:07.182
(wind whistling)

02:07.250 --> 02:08.817
Why didn't you come through the chimney?

02:11.388 --> 02:13.723
What's your name, sweetie?

02:13.791 --> 02:15.558
Susie.
(gasps) Susie.

02:15.626 --> 02:18.094
That's a lovely name.

02:18.162 --> 02:20.898
Well, Susie, none of it
makes much sense, does it, huh?

02:20.965 --> 02:22.699
Flying reindeers,

02:22.767 --> 02:24.468
shimmying down chimneys,

02:24.536 --> 02:27.038
every good Christian house
in the world in one night,

02:27.106 --> 02:28.172
Huh?
(scoffs)

02:28.240 --> 02:29.407
They call me crazy.

02:30.576 --> 02:33.178
Are you hurt, Santa?

02:33.246 --> 02:35.180
Oh, no, no, no, no.

02:35.248 --> 02:36.782
No, this isn't Santa's blood.

02:39.419 --> 02:41.120
You want to take me to Mom and Dad?

02:43.157 --> 02:45.193
Merry Christmas, Daddy.

02:45.260 --> 02:47.862
It's not Christmas yet, baby.

02:47.930 --> 02:50.632
Haven't you been keeping
your advent calendar?

02:50.700 --> 02:52.701
It's wrong. Santa's here.

02:56.273 --> 02:59.008
I think we should all go downstairs.

02:59.076 --> 03:01.511
Milk and cookies time
for you and me, Susie.

03:04.448 --> 03:07.484
What do you want? Money?

03:07.551 --> 03:09.552
I have a safe upstairs, under the bed,

03:09.620 --> 03:11.854
with $5,000 cash in it.

03:11.922 --> 03:13.055
Jewelry, too.
You want to know

03:13.123 --> 03:14.724
why I chose your house?

03:14.792 --> 03:16.025
(crying)

03:16.093 --> 03:17.894
Your Christmas decorations.

03:17.962 --> 03:18.895
("Up on the Housetop" begins)

03:18.963 --> 03:20.531
Christ, man, I mean,

03:20.599 --> 03:23.501
what are you trying
to prove out there, hmm?

03:23.569 --> 03:26.204
What's wrong with a
little Christmas spirit?

03:26.272 --> 03:28.974
You know, you're right.

03:29.041 --> 03:31.410
You're right.

03:31.478 --> 03:34.046
You know what tonight needs?

03:34.114 --> 03:35.848
A little more jingle bells.

03:35.916 --> 03:38.451
(clangs)
Stop! What do you want?

03:38.519 --> 03:40.454
I'm "Santee" Claus!
I'm here to bestow

03:40.521 --> 03:42.056
a little Christmas spirit upon you

03:42.125 --> 03:43.893
because what is Christmas about

03:43.961 --> 03:46.429
if it's not about families
being together?

03:46.496 --> 03:48.931
Do you appreciate that
right now? Do you?

03:48.999 --> 03:50.634
Don't you feel wonderful about being

03:50.701 --> 03:53.071
with your family, huh? Huh?
MAN: Yeah.

03:53.140 --> 03:54.275
Yes? Yes?
Yes.

03:54.343 --> 03:55.444
Yes.
Yes.

03:56.780 --> 03:58.747
So...

03:58.815 --> 04:01.016
I'm gonna tell you
what Santa's gonna leave

04:01.084 --> 04:02.417
under your tree tonight.

04:02.485 --> 04:04.353
He's gonna leave a little terror.

04:04.421 --> 04:06.288
A little rape.

04:06.356 --> 04:07.556
You keep your hands off of her.

04:07.624 --> 04:09.191
Who said anything about her?

04:09.259 --> 04:12.662
You know the difference between
that Santa Claus and me?

04:12.729 --> 04:15.031
He only comes once a year.

04:15.099 --> 04:16.266
Please leave us.

04:16.333 --> 04:19.969
I have to finish my list, huh?

04:20.036 --> 04:22.572
It wouldn't be Christmas
without one big ticket item

04:22.640 --> 04:23.774
from Santa's sack.

04:23.841 --> 04:25.375
And I'm feeling so full

04:25.443 --> 04:28.012
of the Christmas spirit, I...

04:28.079 --> 04:30.080
am gonna let you choose

04:30.148 --> 04:31.115
which one of you

04:31.182 --> 04:32.316
I kill first.

04:32.384 --> 04:33.917
No, please. Stop.

04:33.985 --> 04:35.119
Y-You don't have to do this.

04:35.187 --> 04:36.320
You know what?

04:39.024 --> 04:40.057
I'm not feeling

04:40.125 --> 04:41.993
very Christmassy.

04:43.262 --> 04:44.328
(screaming)

05:40.329 --> 05:51.051
<font color="#ec14bd">Sync & corrections by honeybunny</font>
